msgid "Borlabs Cookie"
msgstr "Borlabs Cookie"

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:64
#: includes/admin/settings-page.php:603
msgid "Real Cookie Banner"
msgstr "Real Cookie Banner"

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:78
msgid "This plugin self-hosts the mave.io player script on your server by default. Videos are embedded with a shortcode, the block editor block, or raw HTML markup."
msgstr "Dieses Plugin hostet das mave.io-Player-Skript standardmäßig auf deinem Server. Videos werden per Shortcode, Block oder HTML-Markup eingebunden."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:79
msgid "Shortcode (recommended for Enfold)"
msgstr "Shortcode (empfohlen für Enfold)"

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:81
#: includes/admin/settings-page.php:702
msgid "HTML markup"
msgstr "HTML-Markup"

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:83
msgid "Use the snippet generator at the bottom of this settings page to copy ready-made examples."
msgstr "Nutze den Snippet-Generator unten auf dieser Seite, um fertige Beispiele zu kopieren."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:84
msgid "Player defaults on this page apply to every embed unless overridden by shortcode or block attributes."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:99
msgid "mave.io does not use tracking cookies. You still need a content blocker for external media because video streams are loaded from mave infrastructure after consent. In Borlabs Cookie 3, set up a provider, a service, and a content blocker, then enable the integration in this plugin."
msgstr "mave.io verwendet keine Tracking-Cookies. Für externe Medien brauchst du trotzdem einen Content Blocker, weil Videostreams nach der Einwilligung von der mave-Infrastruktur geladen werden. In Borlabs Cookie 3: Provider, Service und Content Blocker anlegen, dann die Integration in diesem Plugin aktivieren."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:101
msgid "1. Create a provider (required)"
msgstr "1. Provider anlegen (Pflicht)"

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:102
msgid "Every content blocker must be linked to a provider."
msgstr "Jeder Content Blocker muss mit einem Provider verknüpft sein."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:104
msgid "Open Borlabs Cookie → Consent Management → Providers."
msgstr "Borlabs Cookie → Consent Management → Providers öffnen."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:105
msgid "Click Add New and enter a name, for example “mave.io”."
msgstr "Neu hinzufügen und einen Namen eingeben, z. B. „mave.io“."

#. translators: %s: privacy policy URL link
#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:108
#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:126
#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:194
#, php-format
msgid "Set the privacy policy URL to %s."
msgstr "Datenschutz-URL auf %s setzen."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:111
msgid "Add the provider address if you want it shown in the consent dialog."
msgstr "Provider-Adresse ergänzen, wenn sie im Consent-Dialog angezeigt werden soll."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:112
msgid "Save and activate the provider."
msgstr "Provider speichern und aktivieren."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:115
msgid "2. Create a service (recommended)"
msgstr "2. Service anlegen (empfohlen)"

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:116
msgid "Linking a service to the content blocker allows automatic unblocking for visitors who already accepted that service, and extends the information shown on the blocker preview."
msgstr "Die Verknüpfung mit einem Service ermöglicht automatisches Freigeben für Besucher, die den Service schon akzeptiert haben, und erweitert die Infos in der Blocker-Vorschau."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:118
msgid "Open Borlabs Cookie → Consent Management → Services."
msgstr "Borlabs Cookie → Consent Management → Services öffnen."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:119
msgid "Click Add New (or use the Library if a mave template becomes available later)."
msgstr "Neu hinzufügen (oder später die Library, falls ein mave-Template verfügbar wird)."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:120
#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:189
msgid "Name the service, for example “mave.io video player”."
msgstr "Service benennen, z. B. „mave.io video player“."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:121
msgid "Assign the service to the External Media group."
msgstr "Service der Gruppe Externe Medien zuordnen."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:122
msgid "Select the mave.io provider you created in step 1."
msgstr "Den in Schritt 1 angelegten mave.io-Provider auswählen."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:123
msgid "Describe the purpose: embedding self-hosted mave.io videos. No tracking cookies are set by mave.io."
msgstr "Zweck beschreiben: Einbindung selbst gehosteter mave.io-Videos. mave.io setzt keine Tracking-Cookies."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:129
msgid "Leave cookie definitions empty unless your legal review requires documenting technical session data."
msgstr "Cookie-Definitionen leer lassen, sofern deine Rechtsprüfung keine technischen Session-Daten verlangt."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:130
#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:198
msgid "Save and activate the service."
msgstr "Service speichern und aktivieren."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:133
msgid "3. Create the content blocker"
msgstr "3. Content Blocker anlegen"

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:135
msgid "Open Borlabs Cookie → Content Blocker → Add New."
msgstr "Borlabs Cookie → Content Blocker → Neu hinzufügen."

#. translators: %s: content blocker ID
#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:138
#, php-format
msgid "Set the ID to %s (must match the ID on this settings page)."
msgstr "ID auf %s setzen (muss mit der ID auf dieser Einstellungsseite übereinstimmen)."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:141
msgid "Choose a name, for example “WE Mave Video”."
msgstr "Namen wählen, z. B. „WE Mave Video“."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:142
msgid "In Service information, select the mave.io service from step 2."
msgstr "Unter Service-Informationen den mave.io-Service aus Schritt 2 auswählen."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:143
msgid "In Provider information, select the mave.io provider from step 1 (required)."
msgstr "Unter Provider-Informationen den mave.io-Provider aus Schritt 1 auswählen (Pflicht)."

#. translators: %s: comma-separated hostnames
#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:146
#, php-format
msgid "Under hosts / URLs, add: %s. This blocks external requests until consent."
msgstr "Unter Hosts/URLs ergänzen: %s. Blockiert externe Anfragen bis zur Einwilligung."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:149
msgid "Customize the preview text if needed, for example “Load video” and a short note that mave.io does not use tracking cookies."
msgstr "Vorschautext bei Bedarf anpassen, z. B. „Video laden“ und Hinweis, dass mave.io keine Tracking-Cookies verwendet."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:150
msgid "Activate the content blocker."
msgstr "Content Blocker aktivieren."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:153
msgid "4. Enable this plugin integration"
msgstr "4. Plugin-Integration aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:155
msgid "On this settings page, enable “Wrap player embeds with the Borlabs content blocker”."
msgstr "Auf dieser Seite „Player-Embeds mit dem Borlabs Content Blocker umschließen“ aktivieren."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:156
msgid "Save settings and test a page with a mave embed in a private browser window."
msgstr "Einstellungen speichern und eine Seite mit mave-Embed im privaten Browserfenster testen."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:159
#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:220
msgid "CDN debug mode"
msgstr "CDN-Debug-Modus"

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:160
msgid "No script blocker is required when the player file is self-hosted on your domain. If you enable “Load from official CDN” for debugging, keep the hostnames above so Borlabs can block the external module script until consent."
msgstr "Kein Script Blocker nötig, wenn die Player-Datei auf deiner Domain liegt. Bei „Vom offiziellen CDN laden“ die Hostnames oben beibehalten, damit Borlabs das externe Modul-Skript bis zur Einwilligung blockiert."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:163
msgid "Borlabs Cookie is not active on this site. Install and activate it before using this integration."
msgstr "Borlabs Cookie ist auf dieser Website nicht aktiv. Vor der Integration installieren und aktivieren."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:179
msgid "mave.io does not use tracking cookies. Create a service for external media and let this plugin wait for consent before loading the player."
msgstr "mave.io verwendet keine Tracking-Cookies. Einen Service für externe Medien anlegen; dieses Plugin wartet mit dem Player-Laden auf die Einwilligung."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:181
msgid "1. Create the service"
msgstr "1. Service anlegen"

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:183
msgid "Open Real Cookie Banner → Cookies → Add service (or create from scratch)."
msgstr "Real Cookie Banner → Cookies → Service hinzufügen (oder von Grund auf erstellen)."

#. translators: %s: service unique identifier
#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:186
#, php-format
msgid "Set the unique identifier to %s (must match this settings page)."
msgstr "Eindeutige Kennung auf %s setzen (muss mit dieser Einstellungsseite übereinstimmen)."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:190
msgid "Assign the service to the External media group."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:191
msgid "Describe the purpose: external video hosting via mave.io. No tracking cookies."
msgstr "Zweck: externes Video-Hosting über mave.io. Keine Tracking-Cookies."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:197
msgid "Do not add marketing or statistics cookies for mave.io unless your legal review says otherwise."
msgstr "Keine Marketing- oder Statistik-Cookies für mave.io, sofern deine Rechtsprüfung nichts anderes verlangt."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:201
msgid "2. Optional content blocker in Real Cookie Banner"
msgstr "2. Optionaler Content Blocker in Real Cookie Banner"

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:202
msgid "This plugin already shows a placeholder and defers the player script until consent. You can additionally create a content blocker in Real Cookie Banner if you want RCB to manage blocking by hostname or custom selectors."
msgstr "Dieses Plugin zeigt bereits einen Platzhalter und lädt das Skript erst nach Einwilligung. Optional kannst du in Real Cookie Banner einen Content Blocker für Hostnames oder Selektoren anlegen."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:204
msgid "Open Real Cookie Banner → Cookies → Content blocker → Add content blocker."
msgstr "Real Cookie Banner → Cookies → Content Blocker → Content Blocker hinzufügen."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:205
msgid "Link the blocker to the mave.io service from step 1."
msgstr "Blocker mit dem mave.io-Service aus Schritt 1 verknüpfen."

#. translators: %s: comma-separated hostnames
#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:208
#, php-format
msgid "Suggested hostnames: %s."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:211
msgid "Optional: block custom elements such as mave-player or .we-mave-video-player."
msgstr "Optional: Custom Elements wie mave-player oder .we-mave-video-player blockieren."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:214
msgid "3. Enable this plugin integration"
msgstr "3. Plugin-Integration aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:216
msgid "On this settings page, enable “Wait for Real Cookie Banner consent before loading the player”."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:217
msgid "Save settings and test in a private browser window."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:221
msgid "The integration also works when you load the player script from the official mave CDN. The script is deferred until consent in both cases."
msgstr "Die Integration funktioniert auch mit dem offiziellen mave-CDN. Das Skript wird in beiden Fällen bis zur Einwilligung verzögert."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:222
msgid "If Borlabs Cookie is active and its content blocker integration is enabled, Borlabs takes precedence and Real Cookie Banner integration is skipped."
msgstr "Ist Borlabs Cookie aktiv und die Content-Blocker-Integration eingeschaltet, hat Borlabs Vorrang; die Real-Cookie-Banner-Integration entfällt."

#: includes/admin/settings-help.php:225
msgid "Real Cookie Banner is not active on this site. Install and activate it before using this integration."
msgstr "Real Cookie Banner ist auf dieser Website nicht aktiv. Vor der Integration installieren und aktivieren."

